What is Haarcascade?
A.Haar Cascade is a machine learning-based approach where a lot of positive and negative images are used to train the classifier
We use haar cascade to identify faces in an image or real time video.
Accuracy of haar cascade is around 89%.

The main goal to select a haarcascade model is because it has already predefine model for detect human face and giving a accuracy around 80-95%.

so i want to take to use haarcascade model in my project.





